<p>Hashing</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Key =E2=86=92 memory index</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Symbol tables, caching, DB indexing</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Storage Management</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Efficient memory usage</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Stack, Heap, Contiguous, Linked</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Algorithm Analysis</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
