<h2 id=3D"DataStructuresandAlgorithms-=F0=9F=A7=A95.ChallengesinParallelAlg=
orithms">=F0=9F=A7=A9 <strong>5. Challenges in Parallel Algorithms</strong>=
</h2>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p><strong>Synchronization:</strong> Ensuring tasks coordinate correctly</p=
></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Communication Overhead:</strong> Time spent exchanging data betw=
een processors</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Load Balancing:</strong> Distribute work evenly to avoid idle pr=
ocessors</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Deadlocks / Race Conditions:</strong> Avoid conflicts while acce=
ssing shared resources</p></li>
</ol>
