<p>Example</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>NP</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Solutions verifiable in poly-time</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>May not be solvable in poly-time</p></td>
