<p>Halting problem</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>NP-Complete</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>In NP and NP-Hard</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Solving one =E2=86=92 solve all NP</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
